  "title": "Introduction to Data Structures and Algorithms",
  "lessonText": "This lesson introduces the fundamental concepts of data structures and algorithms.",
  "data": {
    "content": "- Data structures store and organize data.\n- Algorithms are step-by-step procedures for calculations.\n- Understanding both is crucial for efficient programming.\n- Common data structures include arrays, linked lists, and trees.\n- Algorithms can be categorized as sorting, searching, or optimization.\n- Mastery of DSA enhances problem-solving skills."
